OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774029955
OL,3,CMartial artist and actor Chuck Norris
OL,4,Cdies, aged 86
OL,6,FMartial artist and actor Chuck Norris
OL,7,Fhas died at the age of 86, his family
OL,8,Fhas announced on Instagram.
OL,10,FIn a post on Instagram, they said: "It
OL,11,Fis with heavy hearts that our family
OL,12,Fshares the sudden passing of our
OL,13,Fbeloved Chuck Norris yesterday morning.
OL,15,F"While we would like to keep the
OL,16,Fcircumstances private, please know
OL,17,Fthat he was surrounded by his family
OL,18,Fand was at peace.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774029955
OL,3,CMartial artist and actor Chuck Norris
OL,4,Cdies, aged 86
OL,6,F"To the world, he was a martial
OL,7,Fartist, actor, and a symbol of
OL,8,Fstrength. To us, he was a devoted
OL,9,Fhusband, a loving father and
OL,10,Fgrandfather, an incredible brother,
OL,11,Fand the heart of our family."
OL,13,F"He lived his life with faith,
OL,14,Fpurpose, and an unwavering commitment
OL,15,Fto the people he loved. Through his
OL,16,Fwork, discipline, and kindness, he
OL,17,Finspired millions around the world and
OL,18,Fleft a lasting impact on so many lives.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774029955
OL,3,CMartial artist and actor Chuck Norris
OL,4,Cdies, aged 86
OL,6,F"While our hearts are broken, we are
OL,7,Fdeeply grateful for the life he lived
OL,8,Fand for the unforgettable moments we
OL,9,Fwere blessed to share with him.
OL,11,F"The love and support he received from
OL,12,Ffans around the world meant so much to
OL,13,Fhim, and our family is truly thankful
OL,14,Ffor it. To him, you were not just
OL,15,Ffans, you were his friends.
OL,17,F"We know many of you had heard about
OL,18,Fhis recent hospitalisation, and we are
OL,19,Ftruly grateful for the prayers and
OL,20,Fsupport you sent his way.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
