CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774029955
OL,3,CMartial artist and actor Chuck Norris
OL,4,Cdies, aged 86
OL,6,F"As we grieve this loss, we kindly ask
OL,7,Ffor privacy for our family during this
OL,8,Ftime. Thank you for loving him with
OL,9,Fus."
OL,11,FFigures have been paying tribute to
OL,12,FChuck Norris online.
OL,14,FIsrael's Prime Minister Benjamin
OL,15,FNetanyahu posted on X, calling Norris
OL,16,F"a great friend of Israel and a close
OL,17,Fpersonal friend".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
