OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774029955
OL,3,CMartial artist and actor Chuck Norris
OL,4,Cdies, aged 86
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Mike Huckabee, the US
OL,7,Fambassador to Israel, said Norris'
OL,8,Fpassing the "saddest piece of news
OL,9,FI've heard in a while".
OL,11,FPosting on Instagram, British
OL,12,Fstrongman competitor Eddie Hall wrote
OL,13,Fthat he was "gutted" by Norris'
OL,14,Fpassing.
OL,16,F"Absolute legend of a man, we just
OL,17,Fstarted to message each other a little
OL,18,Fon here and was hoping to meet him
OL,19,Fsomeday," he wrote.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
